<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV67">
<l>caṇṭamaṇṭa lattiṉūṭu ceṉṟuvīṭu peṟṟumēl</l>
<l>kaṇṭuvīṭi lātakāta liṉpanāḷu meytuvīr</l>
<l>puṇṭarīka pātapuṇya kīrttinuñce vimaṭuttu</l>
<l>vuṇṭunummu ṟuviṉaittu yaruṇīṅki yuymmiṉō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O you who will obtain the endless bliss of devotion forever</l>
<l>Going through the sun’s orb and obtaining liberation!</l>
<l>Drinking in with your ears and enjoying the purifying glories</l>
<l rend="indent">of the lotus-footed [Lord]</l>
<l>Be saved, being liberated from the karman[-led] sorrow</l>
<l rend="indent">that you are undergoing!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
